#

Spinach Salad with Honey Mustard Dressing

10 min
$10.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickFresh

Description

A refreshing spinach salad topped with crunchy vegetables and a sweet-tangy honey mustard dressing.

Ingredients

  • fresh spinach leaves: 4 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1
  • red onion: 1/4
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
  • dijon mustard: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
